{"type": "article", "id": 10844, "title": "Space case 1 智能行李箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-16T07:15:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125749ltnL8UyR5S4zN0m9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<span>介绍一款开了挂的行李箱，众多功能集一身也许会让人联想到山寨手机的定位，但这些新功能中说不定就有你特别需要的呢，全部功能都能可以由手机上的一个 </span><span>APP</span><span>控制，包括指纹解锁，全球定位追踪和距离传感器不用担心箱子被偷，自称重系统防止超重，箱子顶端有两个插孔能为手机等设备充电，同时箱子还是个蓝牙音响（在酒店的时候可以放点音乐）……箱子的内部也比较构思精妙，最外一层专门为电子产品设计，方便拿进和取出也确保了安全，放得下 </span><span>15.6 </span><span>寸的笔记本电脑。还有一层可以放置套装，用衣架挂一些易皱和易变形的衣服。目前团队正在 </span><span>kickstater </span><span>上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1141432017/space-case-1-the-worlds-most-advanced-smart-suitca?ref=category\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里查看</a>。\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257467dBXr49CsFpeQ2WL.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125747ZLGznQPOedh6DMik.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"413\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60735294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125747yiJITroxMmfg5apC.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"490\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72058824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125748EOSmJlWMKTfuwe7c.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86911765\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125749nIjwtgN9c30M1vBh.jpg\" width=\"708\" height=\"457\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64548023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t</p>\r\n